{
  "total_duration": 657.044,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 11.576,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果一个人钓了一整个上午，一条鱼也没钓到，你会觉得他失败了吗？今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One man in a boat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“独坐孤舟”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 11.926,
      "end": 21.206,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文不是讲“怎样把鱼钓上来”，也不是笑话这个人技术很差。它真正的笑点是：朋友只看结果，他自己享受的是过程。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 21.556,
      "end": 36.139,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先解释一个容易误会的词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fishing is my favourite sport."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不一定是学校比赛或奥运项目，更像"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hobby"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一种户外活动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 36.489,
      "end": 48.145,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fishing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是休闲钓鱼。一个人可以坐在小船上，在河面待一整个上午，不一定是为了吃鱼，也可能只是想安静一下。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 48.495,
      "end": 65.574,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "换成今天的生活，你可以想成：有人玩"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Minecraft"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不一定为了通关；有人画画不一定为了得奖；有人搭"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "LEGO"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不一定为了最快完成。他们喜欢的是慢慢做的感觉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 65.924,
      "end": 77.188,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天抓住这条链："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "no fish, empty bag, friends' scoreboard, quiet boat time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。朋友看“有没有鱼”，他自己要的是“坐在船上，什么也不做”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 77.538,
      "end": 87.418,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，清晨的河面很安静。主人公坐在一只小木船里，带着鱼竿和一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fishing bag"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 87.768,
      "end": 97.759,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他一开头说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fishing is my favourite sport."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "favourite sport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以理解成“我最喜欢的休闲活动”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 98.109,
      "end": 112.261,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I often fish for hours without catching anything."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without catching anything"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“没有钓到任何东西”。可是下一句很关键："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "But this does not worry me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 112.611,
      "end": 119.131,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他没有着急，也没有生气。因为对他来说，坐在船上的安静时间已经很重要。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 119.481,
      "end": 128.368,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，课文拿别的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fishermen"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "做了一个轻轻的夸张对比。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Some fishermen are unlucky."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 128.718,
      "end": 136.246,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他们不是钓到鱼，而是钓到别的东西："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Instead of catching fish, they catch old boots and rubbish."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 136.596,
      "end": 148.836,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "old boots"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是旧靴子，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rubbish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是垃圾。这里不用想得很脏，它更像漫画里的荒唐画面：鱼没来，靴子来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 149.186,
      "end": 160.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Instead of catching fish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很重要："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "instead of"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "catching"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，表示“不是做 A，而是做 B”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 161.191,
      "end": 169.107,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，课文把笑点又往前推一步。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am even less lucky."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他比那些人还“不走运”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 169.457,
      "end": 181.305,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么？因为他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I never catch anything -- not even old boots."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not even"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是“连最低的期待都没有”。连旧靴子都没有。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 181.654,
      "end": 190.27,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后是整篇里最像“成绩单”的画面："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After having spent whole mornings on the river, I always go home with an empty bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 190.62,
      "end": 203.948,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "empty bag"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是空袋子。朋友看到这个结果，就说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You must give up fishing! It's a waste of time."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他们觉得没有鱼，就是浪费时间。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 204.298,
      "end": 211.842,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，真正的答案揭晓。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "But they don't realize one important thing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 212.192,
      "end": 221.071,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "朋友没有意识到重要的一点："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm not really interested in fishing."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他并不是真的对“钓到鱼”这件事感兴趣。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 221.421,
      "end": 228.989,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一行才是全课的机关："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am only interested in sitting in a boat and doing nothing at all!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 229.339,
      "end": 236.859,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以他不是“钓鱼失败”。他成功得到了自己想要的东西：坐在船上，安安静静，什么也不做。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 237.209,
      "end": 241.709,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易误会的地方，是把它当成钓鱼技术课。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 242.059,
      "end": 246.052,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他真的喜欢"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fishing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 246.402,
      "end": 258.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "喜欢，但不是朋友以为的那种喜欢。朋友以为"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fishing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的目标是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "catch fish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他真正喜欢的是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sitting in a boat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 259.119,
      "end": 263.398,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不是比赛？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 263.748,
      "end": 278.108,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为英语里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有时也可以指休闲户外活动。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fishing is my favourite sport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更像“钓鱼是我最喜欢的爱好”，不是“我要赢一场钓鱼比赛”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 278.458,
      "end": 282.386,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "old boots and rubbish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是很恶心？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 282.735,
      "end": 297.039,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不要往那个方向想。这里是轻喜剧的夸张：有些人运气差，鱼没钓到，反而钓到旧靴子和垃圾。它是为了让后面的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not even old boots"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更好笑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 297.389,
      "end": 300.987,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "朋友为什么说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's a waste of time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 301.336,
      "end": 311.316,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为他们只看结果：袋子是空的，没有鱼。可是他们"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "don't realize"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这个人本来就不是为了鱼来河上的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 311.666,
      "end": 316.227,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "doing nothing at all"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是偷懒吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 316.577,
      "end": 325.697,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇里不是。它是安静休息，是从忙碌里抽出来的一段空白时间。结果可以重要，但有些活动的价值也在过程里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 326.047,
      "end": 328.687,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Fishing is my favourite sport."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 329.037,
      "end": 332.565,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I often fish for hours without catching anything."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 332.915,
      "end": 335.315,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "But this does not worry me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 335.664,
      "end": 338.232,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Some fishermen are unlucky."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 338.582,
      "end": 342.566,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Instead of catching fish, they catch old boots and rubbish."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 342.916,
      "end": 345.22,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am even less lucky."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 345.57,
      "end": 348.81,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I never catch anything -- not even old boots."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 349.16,
      "end": 354.248,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After having spent whole mornings on the river, I always go home with an empty bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 354.598,
      "end": 357.766,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'You must give up fishing!' my friends say."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 358.116,
      "end": 360.252,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'It's a waste of time.'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 360.602,
      "end": 363.698,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
