      "end": 575.418,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以是慢慢搭"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "LEGO"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Minecraft"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里乱建房子，安静画画，散步，练琴，投篮，拍照片，或者放学后坐一会儿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 575.767,
      "end": 586.423,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "关键句型可以先听一个完整例子："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am not really interested in winning a prize. I am only interested in drawing quietly and relaxing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 586.773,
      "end": 594.353,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你还可以加一句对比："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My friends think it is a waste of time, but they don't realize that I enjoy the process."
        }
